frankweiler/ui/node_modules
frankweiler/ui/dist
frankweiler/backend/target
# Agent worktrees (Claude Code `isolation: worktree` / spawned tasks) live
# here; each carries its own `bazel-*` convenience symlinks into the bazel
# cache. Without this, `bazel ...` target expansion descends into a nested
# worktree's symlinked external repos and fails to load (`@rules_license`,
# `zlib+`, …).
.claude
